today I’m thinking of @wond3rwoman1’s words from legendary s1 after Makayla Lanvin battled downnnn, maybe the best battle in the series. People speculate about tipping points for ballroom in the mainstream. “Vogue,” Pose, this show, etc. But the thing is ballroom was already mainstream, you just don’t see it. Always referenced, rarely credited, always the moodboard, never the muse, used as foundation, never the pedestal. Legendary was a place ballroom was on the pedestal. And it will be again, but next time the girls will be in the driver’s seat. 🏆
